text: Nandrolone hydrogen succinate (brand name Anabolico, Menidrabol), or nandrolone hemisuccinate, also known as 19-nortestosterone 17β-(3-carboxy)propionate, is a synthetic androgen and anabolic steroid and a nandrolone ester that is or has been marketed in Italy. ==See also== * List of androgen esters § Nandrolone esters ==References== Category:Androgens and anabolic steroids Category:Estranes Category:Nandrolone esters Category:Progestogens Category:Succinate esters Category:Testosterone
title: Nandrolone hydrogen succinate
